title: Muna play "Silk Chiffon" #acoustic
description:
From an August 2022 session at The Current, MUNA perform an acoustic version of the song "Silk Chiffon" off their self-titled album, out now on Saddest Factory Records. 

Find the full session here: https://youtu.be/XFJAk3PTl2Q

title: Killer Mike -- Something For Junkies (live on The Current)
description:
Twenty years into a hip-hop career that includes 10 years as part of the acclaimed group Run The Jewels, Killer Mike has released the solo album, "Michael," (available on @LomaVistaRecs) so that people would get to know the more personal side of Michael Render, “that little nine-year-old boy on the album cover with the horns and the halo and the buck teeth and the smile.”

Watch Killer Mike and the Midnight Revival Choir perform Something For Junkies.

Following the session, Killer Mike sat down with host Jill Riley to share his story. Watch that interview here: https://www.thecurrent.org/feature/2023/08/16/killer-mike-shares-his-music-and-his-story-michael-album
